                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8627" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0205</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1851 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">打造传统船舶制造的数字“共赢链”——崇航供应链的产业互联之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Creating a digital “win-win chain” for traditional shipbuilding: The industry interconnection journey of Chonghang</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘家国，高昕，王军进</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连海事大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">崇航国际供应链管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">船舶制造；数字供应链；产业互联；数实融合；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shipbuilding; Digital supply chain; Industrial interconnection; Integration of digital and real economies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">船舶制造是综合性极强的产业，通过与上下游的广泛联系，对国民经济产生巨大带动作用。同时，船舶制造也拥有着配件多、量级大、工序繁杂的“超级供应链”。为进一步推进我国船舶工业“由大到强”，诸多上下游企业都积极推行数字化，但因上游钢材等大宗物资的批量化、粗线条式生产管理，与总装造船环节的精细化装配及调度模式间存在显著差异，供需两端的数据衔接壁垒使双方始终难以实现深度协同。崇航自2019年起致力于搭建钢厂和船企深度协同的数字供应链，依托GMS全景产业互联平台在上游供方站连接了南钢、宝钢等主流钢厂，在下游总装站嵌入了中船、中远等龙头船企。通过整合产业优势资源，崇航构建了车间级一体化数字供应链与产业互联新模式，成为赋能船舶制造上下游深度协同的“智慧大脑”。截至2024年，平台已实现20余家行业龙头集团的嵌入、234万吨钢材运营支持、40%的效率提升以及9.24%的供应链总持有成本降低。本案例系统梳理了崇航的数字供应链打造过程、阶段成效与未来布局，既描绘了企业践行数实融合发展的典型写照，也为传统船舶工业打造新质生产力提供了现实借鉴与参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shipbuilding, a highly integrated industry, drives the economy by connecting various sectors. It involves a complex “super supply chain” with numerous parts and processes. To strengthen China’s shipbuilding from largest to strongest, digitization is adopted by many enterprises. However, due to the standardized and rougher approach of upstream material production like steel, compared to the refined assembly in shipbuilding, there’s a significant gap in data integration needs, hindering deep collaboration. Since 2019, Chonghang has been building a digital supply chain for deep collaboration between steel mills and shipbuilders. Utilizing the GMS platform, it connects major steel suppliers like Nanjing Iron &amp; Steel and Baowu Group with top shipbuilders such as China Shipbuilding and COSCO Heavy Industry. By integrating resources, Chonghang has developed a workshop-level supply chain and a new interconnection model, becoming the “brain” for deep collaboration. As of 2024, the platform has integrated over 20 leading groups, processed 2.34 million tons of steel, increased efficiency by 40%, and cut holding costs by 9.24%. This case systematically reviews the process of creating Chonghang’s digital supply chain, its phased results, and future plans. It not only depicts a typical portrayal of a company practicing integrated development of digital and physical operations but also provides practical references for the traditional shipbuilding industry to create new productive forces.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《供应链协同运营管理》、《供应链信息管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字供应链的内涵与动因；数字供应链的架构与特征；数字供应链协同的实现路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
